Subject: Silicone Casting for Cheap Bastards
Description: Ever wanted to make things out of silicone but don't want to spend a bunch of money? Learn how to cast things out of inexpensive silicone caulk and corn starch.   Speakers include:Gnora Ford-Lepthien - Track: Costuming  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: Creature Costumes
Description: Learn various techniques to create non-human scifi/fantasy costumes. From scaly to fuzzy, find out how to create a werewolf, lizardman, fishman, insect, and more!  Speakers include:Gnora Ford-Lepthien - Track: Costuming  - Duration: 50 minutes

Subject: Furries!
Description: What is being a furry all about? Find out about your fuzzy friends. Anthropomorphic Characters, Art, & Costumes  Speakers include:Gnora Ford-Lepthien - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes
